author: Jacob Davey
title: Watch Young Thug & Birdman Stunt in New “Bit Bak” Video
text:
If you didn’t already know, Young Thug and Birdman have an upcoming project, entitled Rich Gang II: The Lifestyle , which will be released on April 14. In the lead up to the third installment of the Rich Gang series since Rich Gang: The Tour , the pair have dropped some lavish visuals for the TM-88-produced track.
Directed by frequent Thugger videographer Garfield Larmond, the video finds the Cash Money boss and the Slime Season star stunting in front a Bentley Bentayga, throwing bands of cash over hip-hop’s favorite truck (Future & Migos also have a penchant for mentioning it in their tracks).
It also sees the pair partying with beautiful women in red-neon lit rooms and generally partaking in the usual hip-hop hedonism associated with the duo. Garfield Marmond also directed the candid video for “Safe” – Thugger’s first solo music of 2017, which you can watch below.

In other music news, watch Future join Ariana Grande for the raunchy, sex-filled visuals for “Everyday”.
